		<item>
			<title>Version 1.0b13</title>
 			<description><![CDATA[
 				<p>Thank you for supporting Micro.blog! Here is what's new:</p>
 				<ul style="margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 20px;">
 					<li>Added replies to user profile screen.</li>
 					<li>Added dragging image files to text view to attach them.</li>
 					<li>Improved header spacing, button highlighting, and other layout tweaks.</li>
 					<li>Fixed some actions opening separate copy of app if multiple versions installed.</li>
 					<li>Fixed accidental scrolling behind some headers.</li>
 					<li>Fixed timeline errors not presenting an alert.</li>
 					<li>Removed unused File menu items.</li>
 				</ul>
 			]]></description>
			<pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2017 14:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
			<enclosure url="https://s3.amazonaws.com/micro.blog/mac/Micro.blog_1.0b13.zip" sparkle:shortVersionString="1.0b13" sparkle:version="14" length="2573998" type="application/octet-stream" />
			<sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.12</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
		</item>		

